# The parenthesized call form `(name arg1 arg2 arg3)` may supply an argument for the optional
# parameter that the fixed-arity bare form cannot reach (spec/execution-model.md:316-364; this is
# the `(star 5 100 3)` shape called out in issue #97's acceptance criteria).
define star :size :angle (:sides 5)
  print :size
  print :angle
  print :sides
end
star 10 90
(star 10 90 3)
